# Implementation Plan - Run q-trader

The goal is to run the q-trader project and provide outputs (training and evaluation results).

## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> I need to reinstall dependencies (TensorFlow, NumPy) because the current environment is broken or missing them. I will create a new virtual environment to avoid dirtying the system python.

## Proposed Changes

### Environment Setup
- Create a new virtual environment in `.venv_new`.
- Install `tensorflow` and `numpy`.

### Execution
- Run training for 50 episodes to allow the model to learn more patterns.
- Run evaluation using the model saved at episode 50.

## Verification Plan

### Automated Tests
- Run `python train.py ^GSPC 10 5` to verify training works.
- Run `python evaluate.py ^GSPC_2011 model_ep0` (or latest) to verify evaluation works.

### Manual Verification
- View the terminal output to ensure profit/loss is calculated and model is saved.
